evidence.value: _matomoPaq.push() was used but Matomo tracker was not initialized before the matomo.js file was loaded. Make sure to configure the tracker via _matomoPaq.push before loading matomo.js. Alternatively, you can create a tracker via Matomo.addTracker() manually and then use _matomoPaq.push but it may not fully work as tracker methods may not be executed in the correct order.
